cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is related to natural language processing and machine learning, which are covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it specifically deals with natural language processing. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel deep learning model for sentiment analysis. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper involves developing an AI model for text analysis. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a potential category as sentiment analysis is often used in search engines and recommendation systems. Finally, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper involves designing a neural network architecture.
